20so%20in%20a%20court%20of%20law%20and%20politics%20is%20filled%20with%20wild%20allegations%2C%20but%20here%20there%20are%20videos%20and%20statements%20by%20victims%20against%20the%20JDS%20Hassan%20member%20of%20parliament%20and%2C%20in%20a%20bulldozer%20justice%20era%2C%20the%20least%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20ensured%20is%20he%20is%20questioned%20by%20authorities%20and%20faces%20due%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20group%20of%20over%20100%20intellectuals%20in%20Karnataka%20wrote%20a%20petition%20to%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20seeking%20his%20immediate%20arrest.%20The%20authors%20listed%20a%20few%20demands%20-%20from%20providing%20a%20safe%20environment%20for%20the%20witnesses%2C%20seeking%20immediate%20arrest%20of%20the%20driver%20of%20Prajwal%20(who%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20approached%20some%20political%20leaders%20with%20the%20pen%20drive%20containing%20the%20horrific%20and%20sleazy%20Prajwal%20videos%20)%2C%20demanding%20cases%20to%20be%20booked%20against%20family%20member%20as%20accomplices%20and%20requesting%20interrogation%20of%20politicians%2C%20intelligence%20and%20police%20officials%20who%20may%20have%20colluded%20to%20help%20Prajwal%20leave%20the%20country%20before%20a%20case%20was%20registered%20on%20the%2028th%20of%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20serious%20moral%20questions%20to%20the%20JDS%20on%20why%20it%20hasn't%20forced%20Prajwal%20back%20or%20even%20take%20political%20action%20to%20force%20him%20back.%20It%20seems%20more%20interested%20in%20attacking%20the%20Congress%20for%20leaking%20the%20videos%2C%20who%20leaked%20the%20videos%20by%20itself%20is%20an%20important%20matter%20of%20investigations%20but%20the%20first%20focus%20is%20the%20getting%20their%20MP%20before%20the%20law.%20There%20are%20questions%20over%20the%20BJP%20trying%20to%20distance%20itself%20from%20the%20case%20and%20not%20aggressively%20forcing%20it's%20ally%20the%20JDS%20to%20act%20on%20the%20case.%20Also%2C%20if%20the%20centre%20should%20be%20more%20aggressive%20in%20this%20case.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20questions%20to%20the%20Congress%20which%20rules%20the%20State%20and%20investigators%20if%20they%20are%20treating%20this%20case%20as%20severely%20as%20they%20should.%20Or%20is%20the%20Congress%20looking%20at%20this%20with%20a%20post%20poll%20political%20calculus%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20really%20needs%20rise%20above%20a%20Congress%20Vs%20JDS-BJP%20exchange%20or%20a%20Centre%20versus%20State%20issue.%20There%20are%20crucial%20questions%20over%20whether%20the%20investigators%2C%20prosecutors%20and%20courts%20have%20been%20aggressive%20enough%20in%20this%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20twenty%20days%20on%20we%20are%20still%20only%20at%20a%20blue-collar%20notice.%20There%20are%20questions%20over%20whether%20his%20passport%20ought%20to%20have%20been%20cancelled%20by%20now%20or%20if%20the%20prosecutors%20should%20have%20at%20least%20moved%20the%20court%20for%20an%20order%20to%20impound%20or%20cancel%20his%20passport%20or%20other%20stern%20actions%20to%20force%20him%20back.%20This%20is%20not%20just%20about%20procedural%2C%20legal%20action%20but%20also%20the%20optics%20and%20public%20pressure%20in%20the%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%20Prajwal%20is%20not%20in%20India%2C%20the%20CBI%20becomes%20the%20nodal%20agency%20in%20sending%20requests%20to%20the%20interpol%20to%20have%20notices%20issued.%20From%20a%20pedestrian%20point%20of%20view%2C%20a%20blue%20corner%20notice%20is%20to%20say%20that%20there%20is%20a%20look%20out%20for%20a%20person%2C%20but%20a%20red%20corner%20notice%20is%20declaring%20him%20or%20her%20a%20proclaimed%20offender%2C%20technically%20making%20him%20a%20criminal%20wherever%20he%20or%20she%20is.%20There%20is%20no%20clarity%20on%20what%20steps%20have%20been%20taken%20to%20move%20towards%20such%20a%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20there%20are%20serious%20charges%20like%20rape%20involved%2C%20with%20punishment%20of%20over%207%20years%2C%20there%20is%20no%20arrest%20warrant%20required.%20The%20accused%20could%20face%20direct%20arrest%20anywhere%20in%20India.%20Investigators%20say%20the%20process%20of%20collection%20of%20evidence%20is%20still%20in%20progress%20to%20build%20the%20case%20for%20a%20red%20corner%20notice.%20But%20there%20are%20multiple%20statements%20from%20victims%20that%20have%20been%20recorded%20before%20the%20magistrate%20under%20section%20164%20of%20the%20CRPC.%20In%20rape%20and%20sexual%20assault%20cases%2C%20even%20an%20uncorroborated%20statement%20by%20a%20victim%20has%20significant%20evidentiary%20value%20and%20in%20this%20case%20there%20is%20also%20alleged%20videographic%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECertainly%2C%20all%20sides%20are%20beginning%20to%20seem%20like%20they%20lack%20the%20will%20to%20force%20Prajwal%20back%20to%20even%20merely%20face%20investigations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrajwal's%20father%20H%20D%20Revanna%20was%20arrested%20in%20a%20case%20of%20abduction%20and%20spent%20six%20days%20in%20jail%20before%20being%20released%20on%20bail%20on%20Tuesday.%20He%20faces%20another%20case%20of%20molestation%20as%20well%2C%20where%20he%20has%20been%20granted%20interim%20bail%20and%20final%20order%20is%20expected%20on%2024th.%20There%20are%20concerns%20as%20we%20move%20further%20away%20in%20time%20that%20the%20focus%20on%20the%20case%2C%20and%20hence%20the%20case%20itself%2C%20would%20only%20get%20weaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20JDS%20has%20demanded%20a%20CBI%20probe%20into%20the%20case.%20Prajwal%20clearly%20seems%20to%20be%20biding%20time%20till%20the%20election%20results%20are%20out.%20While%20it%20shouldn't%20matter%20who%20wins%20or%20loses%2C%20the%20fear%20is%20it%20will.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20dangerous%20precedent%20if%20a%20sitting%20MP%20is%20being%20allowed%20to%20dodge%20investigators%20in%20a%20case%20of%20rape%20and%20irrespective%20of%20the%20political%20mud-slinging%2C%20a%20clear%2C%20transparent%20and%20aggressive%20investigation%20is%20the%20least%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20ensured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20vilified%20or%20portrayed%20as%20guilty%20till%20the%20due%20process%20is%20followed%2C%20but%20ensuring%20the%20due%20process%20is%20followed%20is%20a%20responsibility%20of%20the%20State%2C%20the%20Centre%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20BJP%2C%20JDS%2C%20media%20and%20civil%20society.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715919660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fipj1a8jg_prajwal-revanna-pti_625x300_05_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanalysis-systemic-failure-in-forcing-prajwal-revanna-before-investigators-5681696%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Given%20the%20public%20outcry%20and%20mass%20mobilisation%20that%20we%20have%20seen%20over%2C%20at%20least%2C%20some%20high%20profile%20cases%20of%20sexual%20assault%20on%20women%2C%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20asked%20if%20the%20reaction%20to%20the%20Prajwal%20Revanna%20sexual%20crimes%2C%20including%20rape%2C%20case%20has%20been%20muted%2C%20social%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanalysis-systemic-failure-in-forcing-prajwal-revanna-before-investigators-5681696%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanalysis-systemic-failure-in-forcing-prajwal-revanna-before-investigators-5681696%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanalysis-systemic-failure-in-forcing-prajwal-revanna-before-investigators-5681696%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hardik%20T20%20WC%20Selection%20Done%20Under%20Pressure%3F%20Jay%20Shah's%20Remark%20A%20'Hint'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20squad%20saw%20some%20bold%20decisions%20being%20taken%20by%20selectors%20as%20an%20out-of-form%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Hardik%20Pandya%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64177-hardik-himanshu-pandya-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHardik%20Pandya%3C%2Fa%3E%20earned%20the%20nod%20while%20players%20like%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shubman%20Gill%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108578-shubman-gill-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShubman%20Gill%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rinku%20Singh%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F106742-rinku-singh-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERinku%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20snubbed.%20Though%20the%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20chief%20selector%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ajit%20Agarkar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F100-ajit-agarkar-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAjit%20Agarkar%3C%2Fa%3E%20revealed%20in%20a%20press%20conference%20that%20Hardik's%20selection%20was%20down%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20alternatives%2C%20a%20report%20later%20revealed%20that%20the%20selection%20committee%20was%20under%20pressure%20to%20pick%20the%20Mumbai%20Indians%20all-rounder.%20BCCI%20secretary%20Jay%20Shah%20has%20now%20opened%20up%20on%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20squad%20selection%2C%20saying%20players%20can't%20be%20picked%20purely%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20IPL%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20chat%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-mens-t20-world-cup%2Fexclusive-selectors-cant-choose-t20-world-cup-squad-based-on-ipl-alone-says-jay-shah%2Farticleshow%2F110192441.cms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Shah%20asserted%20the%20need%20to%20put%20overseas%20experience%20also%20into%20account%20as%20selectors%20pick%20squads%20for%20a%20tournament%20of%20the%20stature%20of%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20a%20good%20balance%20between%20form%20and%20experience.%20The%20selectors%20cannot%20choose%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20IPL%20performance%20alone%2C%20as%20overseas%20experience%20is%20also%20necessary%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20in%20Dainik%20Jagran%20had%20claimed%20that%20neither%20Rohit%20nor%20the%20selection%20committee%2C%20led%20by%20former%20India%20pacer%20Ajit%20Agarkar%2C%20was%20in%20favour%20of%20selecting%20Hardik.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20added%20that%20Hardik%20was%20picked%20in%20the%20team%20under%20'pressure'.%20The%20report%20did%20not%20mention%20whether%20it%20was%20a%20situational%20pressure%20(as%20he%20is%20India's%20top%20fast%20bowling%20allrounder)%20or%20a%20pressure%20from%20some%20quarters.%20The%20report%20also%20attributed%20sources%20as%20saying%20that%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20%2C%20BCCI%20chief%20selector%20Ajit%20Agarkar%2C%20and%20some%20selectors%20were%20against%20Pandya's%20selection%20in%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20team%2C%20during%20the%20selection%20meeting%20in%20Ahmedabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20team%2C%20at%20present%2C%20doesn't%20have%20a%20pace%20bowling%20all-rounder%20with%20similar%20skillset%20as%20Hardik.%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shivam%20Dube%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107521-shivam-dubey-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShivam%20Dube%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20only%20alternative%20to%20Haridk%2C%20though%20his%20skills%20with%20the%20ball%20don't%20come%20close%20to%20the%20Mumbai%20Indians%20star.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20be%20interesting%20to%20see%20how%20Rohit%2C%20the%20India%20captain%2C%20picks%20his%20playing%20XI%20in%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715919660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fmdok4fm8_agarkar-and-rohit-afp_625x300_03_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fselectors-cant-choose-