eries%2C%20covering%20gas%20and%20electricity%20bills%2C%20offering%20pro%20bono%20plumbing%20services%2C%20and%20even%20assisting%20with%20funeral%20costs%20for%20past%20clients.%20Anderson's%20acts%20of%20charity%20gained%20significant%20public%20attention%2C%20attracting%20financial%20backing%20from%20celebrities%20like%20Hugh%20Grant%20and%20Lily%20Allen.%20He%20even%20secured%20an%20appearance%20on%20ITV's%20%26quot%3BThis%20Morning%26quot%3B%20to%20promote%20his%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc3gxg4jd0ggo%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20investigation%20raises%20questions%20about%20the%20legitimacy%20of%20Depher's%20activities.%20The%20alleged%20misuse%20of%20photos%20and%20the%20disregard%20for%20a%20customer's%20privacy%20cast%20a%20shadow%20on%20Anderson's%20methods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnderson%20prevented%20one%20elderly%20woman%20from%20killing%20herself%2C%20the%20firm%20claimed.%20In%20fact%2C%20she%20had%20died%20years%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20denied%20some%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc3gxg4jd0ggo%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E's%20allegations%20but%20admitted%2C%20%26quot%3BI've%20made%20mistakes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202019%2C%20Depher%20has%20posted%20hundreds%20of%20stories%20about%20acts%20of%20kindness%20it%20says%20it%20has%20carried%20out.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20social%20media%20stories%20made%20him%20a%20viral%20sensation%20during%20the%20UK's%20cost-of-living%20crisis%20and%20brought%20in%20at%20least%202%20million%20pounds%20in%20donations%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%20analysis%20of%20his%20company's%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715918880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Ffcsqmqo8_james-anderson_625x300_17_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fman-dubbed-britains-kindest-plumber-admits-to-fabricating-stories-to-gain-donations-5681789%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20investigation%20reveals%20repeated%20use%20of%20photos%20of%20a%20dead%20woman%20and%20filming%20a%20reluctant%20elderly%20customer%2C%20disregarding%20his%20privacy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fman-dubbed-britains-kindest-plumber-admits-to-fabricating-stories-to-gain-donations-5681789%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fman-dubbed-britains-kindest-plumber-admits-to-fabricating-stories-to-gain-donations-5681789%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fman-dubbed-britains-kindest-plumber-admits-to-fabricating-stories-to-gain-donations-5681789%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22AI%20is%20leading%20to%20the%20'revenge%20of%20the%20liberal%20arts%2C'%20says%20a%20Goldman%20tech%20exec%20with%20a%20history%20degree%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22George%20Lee%20Goldman%20Sachs%20tech%20banking%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6646c4639fc063e829b2172e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22682%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGoldman's%20George%20Lee%20(right)%20studied%20history%20in%20college.%3Cp%3ESportsfile%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGoldman's%20George%20Lee%20said%20AI%20will%20empower%20non-technical%20workers%2C%20including%20those%20in%20risk%20management.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20history%20major%20turned%20tech%20banker%20said%20AI%20enhances%20skills%20like%20critical%20thinking%2C%20creativity%2C%20and%20logic.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBanks%20are%20increasingly%20using%20AI%20for%20fraud%20and%20credit%20risk%20amid%20rising%20regulatory%20demands.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20longtime%20tech%20banker%20with%20a%20history%20degree%20says%20AI%20could%20be%20a%20boon%20for%20non-technical%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGeorge%20Lee%2C%20the%20co-head%20of%20applied%20innovation%20at%20Goldman%20Sachs%2C%20told%20Bloomberg%20Television%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20he%20thinks%20AI%20will%20lead%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Brevenge%20of%20the%20liberal%20arts%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20the%20skills%20that%20are%20really%20salient%20to%20cooperate%20with%20this%20new%20of%20intelligence%20in%20the%20world%20are%20critical%20thinking%2C%20understanding%20logic%20and%20rhetoric%2C%20the%20ability%20to%20be%20creative%2C%26quot%3B%20Lee%20said.%20%26quot%3BAI%20will%20allow%20non-technical%20people%20to%20accomplish%20a%20lot%20more%20%E2%80%94%20and%2C%20by%20the%20way%2C%20begin%20to%20perform%20what%20were%20formerly%20believed%20to%20be%20technical%20tasks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELee%2C%20who%20studied%20history%20at%20Middlebury%20College%20and%20got%20an%20MBA%20from%20the%20Wharton%20School%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Pennsylvania%2C%20sits%20on%20liberal%20arts-focused%20Middlebury's%20board%20of%20trustees.%20He%20joined%20Goldman%20in%201994%20after%20his%20MBA%20and%20was%20previously%20the%20firm's%20co-chief%20information%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELee%20told%20Bloomberg%20that%20AI%20could%20help%20people%20who%20are%20focused%20on%20operations%20and%20risk%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20regulatory%20requirements%20have%20intensified%20globally%20and%20threats%20like%20cybersecurity%20take%20center%20stage%2C%20banks'%20risk%20management%20teams%20have%20swelled.%20In%20an%20annual%20bank%20risk%20management%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ey.com%2Fen_gl%2Findustries%2Fbanking-capital-markets%2Fey-iif-global-bank-risk-management-survey%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurvey%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20EY%20and%20the%20International%20Institute%20of%20Finance%20released%20in%20February%2C%20a%20majority%20of%20banks%20said%20they're%20al