rustles%20up%20come%20and%20go%20without%20always%20being%20convincing%20in%20the%20way%20that%20they%20are%20staged%20or%20in%20the%20manner%20that%20they%20are%20placed%20within%2C%20and%20in%20relation%20to%2C%20the%20'flow'%20of%20the%20saga.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20world-building%20in%20the%20film%20plays%20second%20fiddle%20to%2C%20if%20it%20is%20not%20entirely%20subsumed%20by%2C%20the%20myth%20of%20the%20universe%20that%20George%20Miller%20created%20over%20the%20course%20of%20four%20films%20spread%20over%2045%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20takes%20nearly%20two%20and%20a%20half%20hours%20to%20tell%20the%20origin%20story%20of%20Imperator%20Furiosa%20-%20%3Ci%3EFuriosa%3A%20A%20Mad%20Max%20Saga%3C%2Fi%3E%20is%20longer%20than%20any%20of%20the%20other%20films%20that%20make%20up%20the%20popular%20post-apocalyptic%20war%20drama%20franchise%20-%20but%20that%20is%20not%20necessarily%20the%20only%20aspect%20of%20the%20enterprise%20that%20weighs%20it%20down.%20There%20is%20also%20the%20question%20of%20a%20few%20of%20characters%20not%20being%20accorded%20the%20play%20they%20deserved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20action%20in%20%3Ci%3EFuriosa%3C%2Fi%3E%20straddles%20a%20decade%20and%20a%20half.%20In%20Fury%20Road%20the%20action%20panned%20out%20over%20just%20three%20days.%20It%20is%2C%20therefore%2C%20understandable%20at%20a%20very%20basic%20level%20why%20the%20rhythm%20of%20this%20film%20is%20not%20as%20consistent%20as%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EFuriosa%3A%20A%20Mad%20Max%20Saga%3C%2Fi%3E%20is%20fragmentary%20in%20its%20pacing.%20It%20alternates%20between%20the%20insanely%20whippy%20and%20the%20drably%20predictable%20as%20it%20goes%20from%20being%20dazzlingly%20mounted%20to%20being%20just%20a%20show%20of%20one%20set-piece%20after%20another%20that%20do%20not%20form%20a%20cohesive%20whole.%20It%20traverses%20the%20whole%20spectrum%2C%20leaving%20some%20holes%20that%20prove%20impossible%20to%20plug%20-%20or%20shrug%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%20%3Ci%3EFury%20Road%3C%2Fi%3E%20cast%20its%20spell%20nearly%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20this%20follow-up%20was%20highly%20anticipated.%20But%20notwithstanding%20its%20action%20sequences%20-%20the%20most%20impactful%20one%20plays%20out%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20film%20over%2015-odd%20minutes%20-%20the%20film%20does%20not%20fully%20live%20up%20to%20the%20hype.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorking%20with%20his%20co-screenwriter%20Nico%20Lathouris%2C%20Miller%20pulls%20no%20punches%20in%20handing%20out%20to%20%3Ci%3EFuriosa%3C%2Fi%3E%20what%20she%20deserves%20-%20a%20story%20that%20spans%20from%20the%20time%20that%20she%20is%20an%20innocent%20and%20gutsy%20village%20girl%20to%20the%20point%20in%20her%20life%20when%20she%20has%20channeled%20her%20anger%20and%20thirst%20for%20revenge%20and%20is%20in%20a%20position%20to%20give%20the%20warring%20men%20around%20her%20a%20run%20for%20their%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnya%20Taylor-Joy%20is%20so%20fantastically%20energetic%20yet%20controlled%20as%20the%20titular%20heroine%20that%20even%20when%20images%20of%20Charlize%20Theron%20from%20Fury%20Road%20flash%20across%20our%20minds%20she%20does%20come%20off%20as%20somebody%20who%20might%20wilt%20under%20the%20pressure%20of%20a%20hard%20act%20to%20follow.%20In%20fact%2C%20she%20does%20not%20follow.%20She%20creates%20her%20own%20path.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChris%20Hemsworth%20embodies%20Warlord%20Dementus%2C%20a%20bearded%20and%20long-%20maned%20leader%20of%20a%20marauding%20horde%20of%20bikers%20who%20shows%20a%20softer%20side%20through%20the%20Teddy%20bear%20that%20he%20carries%20in%20order%20to%20remember%20the%20daughter%20he%20lost%2C%20with%20customary%20panache.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDementus%20fights%20a%20running%20war%20with%20Immortan%20Joe%20(Lachy%20Hulme%2C%20replacing%20the%20departed%20Hugh%20Keays-Byrne)%2C%20leader%20of%20the%20Citadel%2C%20the%20powerful%20settlement%20of%20fighters%20that%20were%20in%20pursuit%20of%20Furiosa%20in%20Fury%20Road.%20In%20addition%20to%20Gastown%2C%20the%20second%20fortress%20of%20Wasteland%2C%20and%20the%20Bullet%20Farm%2C%20the%20third%20fortress%2C%20the%20world%20that%20Dementus%20and%20Immortan%20Joe%20inhabit%20are%20perfect%20specimens%20of%20places%20that%20are%20paying%20for%20sins%20of%20men%20past%20and%20present%2C%20They%20struggle%20for%20water%20and%20fuel%20as%20they%20battle%20for%20control%20of%20the%20scarce%20resources%20that%20are%20still%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paucity%20of%20necessities%20in%20the%20Wasteland%20is%20what%20makes%20%3Ci%3EFuriosa%3C%2Fi%3E's%20village%2C%20the%20Green%20Place%20of%20Many%20Mothers%2C%20an%20oasis%20of%20abundance%2C%20a%20sought-after%20location%20whose%20map%20only%20the%20kidnapped%20girl%20who%20has%20grown%20into%20a%20full-blown%20warrior%20possesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20must%20fight%20to%20protect%20the%20secret%20until%20she%20is%20ready%20to%20wreak%20vengeance%20for%20the%20grisly%20killing%20of%20her%20machete-wielding%20mother%20who%20did%20everything%20in%20her%20power%20to%20save%20Furiosa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EFuriosa%3A%20A%20Mad%20Max%20Saga%3C%2Fi%3E%20is%20low%20on%20emotional%20power%20because%20the%20protagonist's%20struggle%20to%20find%20her%20way%20back%20home%20forces%20her%20into%20too%20many%20detours.%20By%20the%20time%20she%20and%20Dementus%20face%20off%20and%20the%20girl%20demands%20her%20childhood%20and%20her%20mother%20back%2C%20the%20film%20has%20lost%20its%20ability%20to%20catch%20us%20by%20surprise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FFVswuip0-co%3Fsi%3DBrTADWtVKTOF_jc0%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20audience%20keeps%20waiting%20for%20the%20confrontation.%20It%20comes%20way%20too%20late%20in%20the%20narrative%20arc.%20The%20words%20Furiosa%20and%20Dementus%20exchange%20do%20serve%20the%20purpose%20of%20rounding%20off%20the%20tale%2C%20but%20the%20film%20has%20several%20moments%20when%20the%20lines%20spoken%20are%20drowned%20out%20by%20the%20music%20or%20the%20sound%20effects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20other%20disappointment%20in%20the%20film%20is%20the%20short%20shrift%20given%20to%20Tom%20Burke.%20The%20actor%20plays%20Praetorian%20Jack%2C%20who%20forms%20a%20partnership%20with%20Furiosa%20but%20he's%20gone%20as%20suddenly%20as%20he%20appears%2C%20leaving%20behind%20no%20real%20traces%20of%20the%20hint%20of%20romance%20that%20develops%20between%20the%20two%20characters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20the%20bikes%2C%20the%20war%20rig%20and%20the%20other%20moving%20contraptions%20that%20the%20film%20uses%2C%20many%20of%20its%20warriors%20are%20flashes%20that%20are%20only%20momentary.%20While%20some%20of%20them%20make%20an%20impression%20is%20their%20respective%20stray%20little%20pockets%2C%20they%20do%20aren't%20linked%20with%20each%20other%20in%20completely%20meaningful%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHardcore%20fans%20of%20%3Ci%3EMad%20Max%3C%2Fi%3E%20will%20find%20a%20great%20deal%20to%20like%20here%2C%20but%20if%20you%20are%20the%20sort%20of%20filmgoer%20who%20expects%20much%20more%20from%20George%20Miller%2C%20you%20will%20be%20left%20feeling%20shortchanged.%20This%20Mad%20Max%20saga%20is%20mad%20enough%20but%20it%20isn't%20driven%20by%20the%20sort%20of%20manic%20force%20that%20propelled%20%3Ci%3EFury%20Road%3C%2Fi%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715916300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F9nd064b8_furiosa_625x300_17_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Ffuriosa-a-mad-max-saga-review-spectacular-and-sporadically-exhilarating-2-5-stars-5681597%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Furiosa%3A%20A%20Mad%20Max%20Saga%20premiered%20Out%20of%20Competition%20on%20Wednesday%20evening%20at%20the%2077th%20Cannes%20Film%20Festival.%20It%20is%20sched