6_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fworld-news%2Fnumber-of-ultra-rich-grows-more-worth-over-100-bn-than-ever-before-124051700056_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Proposes%20Historic%20Law%20To%20Reclassify%20Marijuana%20As%20%26quot%3BLow-Risk%20Drug%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20administration%20formally%20proposed%20on%20Thursday%20reclassifying%20marijuana%20as%20a%20less%20dangerous%20drug%2C%20a%20historic%20shift%20that%20would%20bring%20federal%20policy%20more%20in%20line%20with%20public%20opinion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20one%20should%20be%20in%20jail%20merely%20for%20using%20or%20possessing%20marijuana.%20Period%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20said%20in%20a%20video%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFar%20too%20many%20lives%20have%20been%20upended%20because%20of%20a%20failed%20approach%20to%20marijuana%20and%20I'm%20committed%20to%20righting%20those%20wrongs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarijuana%20has%20been%20classified%20since%201970%20as%20a%20so-called%20Schedule%20I%20drug%20under%20the%20Controlled%20Substances%20Act%20(CSA)%20--%20the%20same%20level%20as%20with%20heroin%2C%20ecstasy%20and%20LSD.%20That%20classification%20means%20it%20is%20deemed%20to%20have%20no%20accepted%20medical%20use%20and%20a%20high%20potential%20for%20abuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20would%20be%20downgraded%20to%20a%20Schedule%20III%20drug%20under%20the%20proposal%2C%20putting%20it%20alongside%20drugs%20like%20ketamine%20and%20painkillers%20containing%20codeine%2C%20considered%20to%20have%20a%20moderate%20to%20low%20likelihood%20of%20dependence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20wouldn't%20make%20it%20legal%2C%20but%20it%20could%20lead%20to%20fewer%20arrests%20at%20the%20federal%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposal%20to%20reclassify%20cannabis%20was%20unveiled%20by%20the%20Biden%20administration%20at%20the%20end%20of%20April%20and%20the%20Justice%20Department%20officially%20launched%20the%20process%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarijuana%20will%20remain%20a%20controlled%20substance%20until%20the%20process%20--%20which%20includes%20a%20public%20comment%20period%20and%20a%20potential%20hearing%20before%20a%20judge%20--%20is%20complete.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20Biden%20became%20the%20first%20president%20to%20initiate%20a%20federal%20review%20of%20marijuana%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERacist%20past%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20potential%20vote%20winner%20for%20Biden%20as%20he%20faces%20Republican%20Donald%20Trump%20in%20a%20tough%20election%20rematch%20this%20November%2C%20especially%20among%20younger%20people%20that%20the%20Democratic%20incumbent%20is%20struggling%20to%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Pew%20Research%20Center%20survey%20found%2088%20percent%20of%20Americans%20believe%20marijuana%20should%20be%20legal%20for%20medical%20or%20recreational%20use.%20Just%2011%20percent%20said%20it%20should%20not%20be%20legal%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECannabis%20was%20first%20outlawed%20at%20the%20federal%20level%20in%201937%2C%20a%20decision%20critics%20say%20was%20made%20largely%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20racist%20ideas%2C%20as%20the%20drug%20was%20perceived%20as%20being%20intimately%20tied%20to%20jazz%20music%2C%20the%20Black%20community%20and%20Mexican%20immigrants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%201970s%20brought%20the%20%26quot%3BWar%20on%20Drugs%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20likewise%20disproportionately%20hit%20minorities%20--%20before%20the%20medical%20marijuana%20movement%20took%20root%20in%20the%201990s.%20In%202012%2C%20US%20states%20began%20to%20make%20recreational%20cannabis%20legal%20for%20adults.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECannabis%20is%20today%20a%20multibillion-dollar%20business%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20with%20more%20than%20half%20of%20all%20states%20having%20legalized%20recreational%20and%20medicinal%20cannabis%20use%2C%20including%20California%20and%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20figures%20show%20that%20racial%20minorities%2C%20in%20particular%20Black%20Americans%2C%20are%20overrepresented%20in%20marijuana-related%20arrests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20decision%20is%20monumental%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20NAACP%20civil%20rights%20organization%20said%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFar%20too%20many%20Black%20Americans%20have%20fallen%20victim%20to%20a%20system%20designed%20for%20their%20demise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBoost%20to%20legal%20industry%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20drug%20remains%20a%20controlled%20substance%20at%20the%20national%20level%2C%20everyone%20involved%20is%20still%20technically%20breaking%20the%20law%20of%20the%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20classification%20makes%20it%20difficult%20for%20businesses%20in%20the%20marijuana%20industry%20to%20access%20banking%20services%2C%20stops%20federal%20funding%20for%20medical%20marijuana%20research%20and%20prevents%20interstate%20commerce%20as%20well%20as%20federal%20regulation%20on%20best%20practices%20and%20protocols%20for%20marijuana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20reclassification%20would%20also%20allow%20companies%20to%20deduct%20their%20operating%20expenses%20from%20their%20taxes%2C%20which%20is%20currently%20prohibited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThursday's%20decision%20%26quot%3Bwill%20unlock%20important%20research%20on%20the%20medical%20efficacy%20of%20cannabis%20and%20bring%20about%20real%20change%20for%20legal%20operators%2C%26quot%3B%20Curaleaf%20CEO%20Matt%20Darin%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wall%20Street%2C%20industry%20shares%20rose%2C%20with%20Curaleaf%20gaining%201.07%20percent%20and%20Verano%20Holdings%20.69%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%2