0and%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-online-financial-advisors%5C%22%3Efinancial%20advisor%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20planner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20professionals%20can%20help%20you%20by%20providing%20expert%20advice%20and%20tangible%20action%20steps%20to%20follow%2C%20their%20true%20value%20may%20lie%20more%20in%20intangible%20factors%2C%20including%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHelping%20you%20to%20control%20your%20emotions.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20No%20matter%20how%20wealthy%20you%20are%2C%20losing%20your%20cool%20can%20happen%20to%20the%20best%20of%20us.%20My%20most%20successful%20clients%20lean%20on%20us%20to%20help%20them%20separate%20those%20emotions%20and%20make%20sound%20financial%20decisions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EProviding%20a%20clear%20road%20map%20when%20there%20are%20endless%20paths%20to%20explore.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20My%20most%20successful%20clients%20value%20receiving%20comprehensive%20financial%20plans%20specific%20to%20their%20goals%20and%20situations.%20They%20use%20these%20plans%20to%20help%20prioritize%20their%20goals%20and%20create%20cash-flow%20strategies%20that%20maximize%20savings%20or%20optimize%20distribution%20strategies.%20In%20addition%2C%20they%20lean%20on%20these%20plans%20to%20assess%20their%20risk%20exposure.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EKeeping%20up%20with%20rapidly%20changing%20financial%20and%20legal%20landscapes.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20the%20field%20of%20finance%2C%20things%20are%20forever%20changing%20because%20of%20new%20legislation%2C%20groundbreaking%20research%2C%20and%20new%20products.%20I'd%20argue%20that%20since%20December%202017%20we%20have%20had%20the%20most%20legislative%20changes%20our%20industry%20has%20ever%20seen.%20Some%20of%20those%20recent%20legislative%20changes%20include%20the%20Tax%20Cut%20and%20Jobs%20Act%20(enacted%20in%20December%202017)%2C%20the%20Setting%20Every%20Community%20Up%20for%20Retirement%20Enhancement%20Act%20(enacted%20in%20Dec