%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Top%20Court's%20Order%20On%20Acquiring%20Private%20Property%2C%20A%20%26quot%3BProcedure%26quot%3B%20Caveat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECompulsory%20acquisition%20of%20private%20properties%20will%20be%20unconstitutional%20if%20proper%20procedure%20is%20not%20established%20or%20followed%20before%20depriving%20a%20person%20of%20their%20right%20to%20property%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20significant%20verdict%2C%20the%20top%20court%20said%20even%20the%20statutory%20scheme%20of%20payment%20of%20compensation%20in%20return%20for%20acquisition%20of%20private%20properties%20will%20not%20be%20justified%20if%20the%20due%20procedure%20is%20not%20followed%20by%20the%20state%20and%20its%20instrumentalities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20making%20the%20observations%2C%20a%20bench%20comprising%20justices%20PS%20Narasimha%20and%20Aravind%20Kumar%20dismissed%20the%20appeal%20of%20the%20Kolkata%20Municipal%20Corporation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20civic%20body%20had%20approached%20the%20top%20court%20challenging%20the%20judgment%20of%20a%20division%20bench%20of%20the%20Kolkata%20High%20Court%20which%20had%20quashed%20acquisition%20of%20a%20property%20at%20Narkeldanga%20North%20Road%20in%20the%20city%20for%20constructing%20a%20park.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20had%20held%20that%20the%20civic%20body%20had%20no%20power%20under%20a%20specific%20provision%20to%20go%20for%20compulsory%20acquisition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20of%20the%20considered%20opinion%20that%20the%20High%20Court%20was%20fully%20justified%20in%20allowing%20the%20writ%20petition%20and%20rejecting%20the%20case%20of%20the%20appellant-Corporation%20acquiring%20land%20under%20Section%20352%20of%20the%20Act.%20The%20impugned%20judgment%20does%20not%20brook%20interference%20on%20any%20count%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20top%20court%20said%20in%20its%2032-page%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnder%20our%20constitutional%20scheme%2C%20compliance%20with%20a%20fair%20procedure%20of%20law%20before%20depriving%20any%20person%20of%20his%20immovable%20property%20is%20well%20entrenched%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Narasimha%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAgain%2C%20assuming%20that%20Section%20363%20of%20the%20Kolkata%20Municipal%20Corporation%20Act%20provides%20for%20compensation%2C%20compulsory%20acquisition%20will%20still%20be%20unconstitutional%20if%20proper%20procedure%20is%20not%20established%20or%20followed%20before%20depriving%20a%20person%20of%20their%20right%20to%20property%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20undue%20emphasis%20is%20laid%20on%20the%20provisions%20of%20compensation%20to%20justify%20the%20power%20of%20compulsory%20acquisition%2C%20as%20if%20compensation%20by%20itself%20is%20the%20complete%20procedure%20for%20a%20valid%20acquisition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20it%20is%20true%20that%20after%20the%2044th%20Constitutional%20Amendment%2C%20the%20right%20to%20property%20drifted%20from%20Part%20III%20(fundamental%20rights)%20to%20Part%20XII%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20there%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20potent%20safety%20net%20against%20arbitrary%20acquisitions%2C%20hasty%20decision-making%20and%20unfair%20redressal%20mechanisms%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Article%20300A%20(right%20to%20property)%20of%20the%20Constitution%20says%20that%20%26quot%3Bno%20person%20shall%20be%20deprived%20of%20his%20property%20save%20by%20authority%20of%20law%26quot%3B%20and%20it%20has%20been%20characterised%20both%20as%20a%20constitutional%20and%20a%20human%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20assume%20that%20constitutional%20protection%20gets%20constricted%20to%20the%20mandate%20of%20a%20fair%20compensation%20would%20be%20a%20disingenuous%20reading%20of%20the%20text%20and%2C%20shall%20we%20say%2C%20offensive%20to%20the%20egalitarian%20spirit%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20there%20are%20seven%20sub-rights%20which%20can%20be%20identified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%3A%20i)%20duty%20of%20the%20State%20to%20inform%20the%20person%20that%20it%20intends%20to%20acquire%20his%20property%20-%20the%20right%20to%20notice%2C%20ii)%20the%20duty%20of%20the%20State%20to%20hear%20objections%20to%20the%20acquisition%20-%20the%20right%20to%20be%20heard%2C%20iii)%20the%20duty%20of%20the%20State%20to%20inform%20the%20person%20of%20its%20decision%20to%20acquire%20-%20the%20right%20to%20a%20reasoned%20decision%2C%20iv)%20the%20duty%20of%20the%20State%20to%20demonstrate%20that%20the%20acquisition%20is%20for%20public%20purpose%20-%20the%20duty%20to%20acquire%20only%20for%20public%20purpose%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B(v)%20the%20duty%20of%20the%20State%20to%20restitute%20and%20rehabilitate%20-%20the%20right%20of%20restitution%20or%20fair%20compensation%2C%20vi)%20the%20duty%20of%20the%20State%20to%20conduct%20the%20process%20of%20acquisition%20efficiently%20and%20within%20prescribed%20timelines%20of%20the%20proceedings%20-%20the%20right%20to%20an%20efficient%20and%20expeditious%20process%2C%20and%20vii)%20final%20conclusion%20of%20the%20proceedings%20leading%20to%20vesting%20-%20the%20right%20of%20conclusion%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20seven%20rights%20are%20foundational%20components%20of%20a%20law%20that%20is%20in%20tune%20with%20Article%20300A%2C%20and%20the%20absence%20of%20one%20of%20these%20or%20some%20of%20them%20would%20render%20the%20law%20susceptible%20to%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715884800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-07%2Fatt9hsso_court-generic_625x300_27_July_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-supreme-courts-order-on-acquiring-private-property-a-procedure-caveat-5679943%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Compulsory%20acquisition%20of%20private%20properties%20will%20be%20unconstitutional%20if%20proper%20procedure%20is%20not%20established%20or%20followed%20before%20depriving%20a%20person%20of%20their%20right%20to%20property%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20on%20Thursday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-supreme-courts-order-on-acquiring-private-property-a-procedure-caveat-5679943%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-supreme-courts-order-on-acquiring-private-property-a-procedure-caveat-5679943%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-supreme-courts-order-on-acquiring-private-property-a-procedure-caveat-5679943%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BLike%20New%20Birth%20Certificates%20For%20Us%26quot%3B%3A%20Man%20Who%20Got%20Citizenship%20Under%20CAA%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20%26quot%3Bnew%20birth%20certificates%26quot%3B.%20This%20is%20how%20Dayal%20Singh%2C%20a%20refugee%20from%20Pakistan%2C%20described%20the%20citizenship%20certificates%20issued%20to%20him%2C%20his%20son%20and%20his%20daughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%2C%2047%2C%20who%20has%20been%20living%20in%20a%20shanty%20in%20North%20Delhi's%20Majnu-ka-Tilla%20since%202013%20after%20he%20migrated%20from%20Pakistan%20with%20his%20family%2C%20was%20among%20the%2014%20people%20to%20be%20given%20the%20certificate%20under%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%20(CAA)%20on%20Wednesday.%20The%20law%20grants%20Indian%20nationality%20to%20persecuted%20non-Muslim%20migrants%20from%20Pakistan%2C%20Afghanistan%20and%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh's%20wife%20Mira%2C%2040%2C%20and%20his%20other%20five%20children%20are%20yet%20to%20get%20their%20certificates%20but%20she%20is%20happy%20that%20a%20part%20of%20the%20family%20is%20now%20'Bharatiya%20Nagriks'%20(Indian%20citizens).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20journey%20was%20filled%20with%20challenges%20due%20to%20the%20identity%20we%20carried%20with%20us.%20But%20now%20we%20are%20'Bharatiya%20Nagriks'%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mira%20while%20talking%20to%20PTI%20in%20the%20shanty%20that%20is%20part%20of%20a%20camp%20for%20refugees%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20stay%20in%20tents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20are%20engaged%20in%20odd%20jobs%20such%20as%20selling%20chips%20and%20other%20packed%20food%20items%2C%20water%20bottles%20and%20mobile%20phone%20covers%20on%20the%20roadside%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%20%26quot%3BMy%20father-in-law%20used%20to%20always%20say%20'One%20day%20we%20will%20be%20called%20Bharatiyas%20and%20that%20will%20be%20the%20biggest%20day%20of%20our%20lives'.%20He%20died%20waiting%20for%20that%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Mira%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20will%20be%20happy%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20migrant%20family%20at%20the%20camp%20has%20endured%20years%20of%20hardship%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHere%2C%20two%20or%20three%20families%20with%2015-20%20people%20live%20together%20in%20cramped%20conditions%20with%20minimal%20resources.%20We%20started%20getting%20our%20children%20married%20off%20quickly%20to%20secure%20their%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20citizenship%20certificates%20were%20handed%20over%20to%20Singh%2C%20his%20son%20Bharat%20Kumar%20and%20daughter%20Yashoda%2C%20and%20the%2011%20others%20by%20the%20Union%20home%20secretary%20after%20their%20applications%20were%20processed%20online%20through%20a%20designated%20portal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20day%20of%20celebration%2C%20Jhula%20Ram%2C%20who%20migrated%20from%20Pakistan's%20Sindh%20province%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20took%20our%20first%20step%20in%20India%20on%20October%205%2C%202013.%20Yesterday%2C%20we%20became%20citizens%20of%20this%20country.%20Our%20family%20has%2018%20members%2C%20and%20three%20of%20us%20have%20received%20our%20'birth%20certificates'%20(citizenship%20certificates)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReflecting%20on%20his%20life%20in%20Sindh%2C%20Ram%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20young%20at%20that%20time%20but%20we%20used%20to%20live%20in%20a%20tense%20atmosphere.%20Whenever%20something%20happened%20against%20them%2C%20we%20used%20to%20become%20targets%2C%20and%20we%20were%20threatened.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BNear%20my%20house%20(in%20Pakistan)%2C%20there%20was%20a%20temple%20of%20Devi%20Maa%2C%20which%20I%20still%20miss%20as%20it%20is%20one%20of%20my%20only%20good%20memories%20from%20childhood.%20I%20do%20miss%20that%20temple%20but%20now%20I'll%20start%20going%20to%20Vaishno%20Devi%20(in%20Jammu)%2C%26quot%3B%20Ram%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERam%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOur%20children%20will%20be%20proud%20and%20happy%20with%20the%20decision%20we%20made.%20It%20will%20eventually%20make%20their%20lives%20easier.%26quot%3B%20Expressing%20gratitude%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20Mira%20said%20the%20new%20identity%20will%20secure%20the%20future%20of%20her%20family.%20She%20has%20named%20her%20youngest%20daughter%2C%2014%2C%20after%20the%20late%20actor%20Sridevi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%2058-year-old%20resident%20of%20the%20camp%2C%20who%20did%20not%20want%20to%20be%20identified%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20came%20here%20in%202015%2C%20and%20as%20per%20the%20CAA%2C%20only%20those%20who%20came%20to%20India%20on%20or%20before%20December%2031%2C%202014%2C%20will%20get%20the%20CAA's%20benefits.%26quot%3B%20Shantaram%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOur%20people%20are%20being%20accepted%20and%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20called%20refugees.%20People%20call%20us%20Pakistani%20refugees%20but%20now%20we%20will%20be%20called%20Indians.%20However%2C%20my%20family%20and%20I%20came%20in%202015.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BI%20run%20a%20shop%20here%20and%20am%20just%20making%20a%20living.%20I%20have%2050%20members%20in%20my%20family%2C%20and%20we%20are%20all%20in%20the%20same%20situation%2C%20not%20knowing%20what%20we%20will%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20The%20CAA%20was%20enacted%20in%20December%202019%20to%20grant%20Indian%20nationality%20to%20persecuted%20Hindu%2C%20Sikh%2C%20Jain%2C%20Buddhist%2C%20Parsi%20and%20Christian%20migrants%20from%20Bangladesh%2C%20Pakistan%20and%20Afghanistan%20who%20came%20to%20India%20on%20or%20before%20December%2031%2C%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20enactment%2C%20the%20CAA%20got%20the%20president's%20assent%20but%20the%20rules%20under%20which%20the%20Indian%20citizenship%20was%20granted%20were%20issued%20on%20March%2011%20this%20year%20after%20over%20a%20delay%20of%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20the%20decades-long%20wait%20of%20those%20who%20faced%20religious%20persecution%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20Bangladesh%20and%20Afghanistan%20is%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715884200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fbb11gfd_caa-_625x300_16_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flike-new-birth-certificates-for-us-man-who-got-citizenship-under-caa-5679912%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22These%20are%20%26quot%3Bnew%20birth%20certificates%26quot%3B.%20This%20is%20how%20Dayal%20Singh%2C%20a%20refugee%20from%20Pakistan%2C%20described%20the%20citizenship%20certificates%20issued%20to%20him%2C%20his%20son%20and%20his%20daughter.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flike-new-birth-certificates-for-us-man-who-got-citizenship-under-caa-5679912%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%