Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recipes%20are%20all%20hers%2C%20given%20to%20her%20by%20her%20grandmother.%20%E2%80%9CI%20oversee%20the%20cooking%20from%20time%20to%20time.%20I%20ensure%20no%20compromise%20there.%20Everything%20is%20made%20with%20love%20and%20care%20with%20the%20best%20ingredients%20%E2%80%94%20just%20like%20the%20way%20I%20would%20make%20for%20my%20own%20family%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Paati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPaati%20also%20enjoys%20making%20Instagram%20reels%20and%20sharing%20her%20love%20for%20M%20S%20Dhoni!%20Bursting%20with%20enthusiasm%20for%20this%20phase%20of%20life%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20like%20a%20rebirth%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENailini%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20energy%20that%20Janaki%20Paati%20brings%20to%20everything%20she%20does%20is%20truly%20contagious%3B%20whether%20it%20is%20cheering%20on%20her%20favourite%20cricketer%20or%20learning%20the%20latest%20mobile%20apps%2C%20her%20passion%20and%20zest%20for%20life%20are%20unparalleled.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20startup%20has%20expanded%20not%20only%20pan-India%20but%20to%2032%20countries%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fchennai%2Fsuccess-is-sweet-and-savoury%2Farticleshow%2F105527913.cms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESuccess%20is%20sweet%20and%20savoury%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20by%20Sindhu%20Hariharan%20for%20Times%20of%20India%2C%20Published%20on%2027th%20November%2C%202023%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Ffeed%2Fupdate%2Furn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A7183872808127508482%2F%5C%22%20targ