20was%20a%20humble%20boy%20who%20ascended%20the%20throne%20because%20of%20his%20quick%20wit.%20In%201870%2C%20Maharaja%20Khanderao%20Gaekwad%20II%20passed%20away%2C%20leaving%20behind%20his%20widow%20who%20decided%20to%20start%20looking%20for%20an%20heir.%20She%20called%20the%20heads%20of%20the%20extended%20family%20of%20Gaekwad%20to%20Baroda%20deciding%20to%20screen%20the%20youngsters%20with%20a%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Shrimant%20Kashirao%20Gaekwad%20presented%20himself%20before%20the%20queen%20with%20his%20three%20sons%2C%20she%20asked%20them%20the%20purpose%20of%20their%20arrival.%20It%20was%20Gopalrao%E2%80%99s%20answer%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20come%20here%20to%20rule%E2%80%9D%2C%20that%20amused%20the%20queen%20and%20she%20made%20him%20heir%20to%20the%20throne.%20The%20young%20boy%20came%20to%20be%20known%20as%20Maharaja%20Sayajirao%20Gaekwad%20III.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715321128000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FMaharani_Vani_Vilasa_with_grandson_Jayachamarajendra_Wadiyar_11zon-1715148493.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D349250%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22They%20say%20a%20moment%20can%20change%20the%20course%20of%20history.%20Here's%20exploring%20bold%2C%20compelling%2C%20and%20introspective%20moments%20from%20our%20past%20that%20shaped%20the%20India%20of%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F349250%2Fhistory-in-pictures-first-elections-voting-for-women-shivaji-maharaj-hussainiwala-mysuru-queen-chetak%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Just%20Slow%20Down%E2%80%99%3A%20Couple%20Quit%20City%20Life%20to%20Build%20Bamboo%20Homestay%20Surrounded%20by%20Nature%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20sound%20of%20crickets%20chirpin