0the%20area%20were%20being%20modernised.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20old-school%20mud%20homes%20with%20sloping%20bamboo%20roofs%2C%20which%20were%20the%20essence%20of%20the%20area%2C%20were%20all%20gone.%20In%20losing%20our%20traditional%20architecture%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20losing%20the%20customs%20and%20traditions%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWanting%20to%20preserve%20the%20traditional%20culture%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20use%20a%20traditional%20technique%20called%20Irka%20to%20make%20the%20home.%20%E2%80%9CEssentially%2C%20what%20the%20technique%20involves%20is%20using%20bamboo%2C%20wood%20and%20mud%20to%20make%20the%20home.%20The%20mud%2C%20mixed%20with%20dung%20and%20straw%2C%20is%20plastered%20on%20a%20wooden%20frame%20woven%20with%20bamboo%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Kabir%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20made%20mud%20bricks%20which%20are%20baked%20in%20the%20sun.%20We%20used%20the%20land%20from%20our%20own%20property%20which%20helped%20us%20reduce%20our%20carbon%20footprint.%20We%20were%20really%20conscious%20of%20the%20impact%20we%20have%20on%20the%20nature%20around%20us.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Ahana%20also%20points%20out%20that%20another%20reason%20to%20use%20mud%20is%20that%20it%20is%20a%20natural%20coolant.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20temperatures%20in%20these%20areas%20have%20typically%20been%20low%2C%20we%20are%20seeing%20hotter%20days%20now.%20We%20wanted%20to%20use%20a%20method%20that%20keeps%20the%20house%20cool%20naturally%20which%20is%20why%20we%20used%20mud%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20588px)%20100vw%2C%20588px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FGuest-cottage-2-1-1-1715264113.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22588%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20place%20is%20a%20short%20walk%20away%20from%20a%20riverside%20where%20you%20can%20enjoy%20picnic%20with%20your%20family.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FGuest-cottage-2-1-1-1715264113.jpg%20588w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FGuest-cottage-2-1-1-1715264113-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FGuest-cottage-2-1-1-1715264113-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FGuest-cottage-2-1-1-1715264113-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349522%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22441%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20place%20is%20a%20short%20walk%20away%20from%20a%20riverside%20where%20you%20can%20enjoy%20picnic%20with%20your%20family.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20homestay%20currently%20has%20two%20ensuite%20rooms%20and%20a%20common%20dining%20area.%20The%20property%20is%20located%20on%203.5%20acres%20of%20paddy%20and%20maize%20fields.%20It%20offers%20scenic%20outdoors%20with%20a%20glimpse%20into%20the%20mountain%20farm%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20multiple%20lawns%20for%20you%20to%20take%20walks%20in%20and%20a%20gazebo-style%20seating%20area%20where%20you%20can%20sip%20delicious%20Darjeeling%20tea%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kabir.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20being%20made%20with%20natural%20materials%2C%20the%20homestay%20also%20follows%20an%20eco-friendly%20philosophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20minimise%20the%20use%20of%20practice.%20We%20encourage%20our%20guests%20not%20to%20bring%20their%20own%20water%20as%20we%20provide%20them%20with%20filtered%20water%20over%20bottled%20water.%20We%20also%20compost%20all%20our%20kitchen%20waste%20and%20leaves.%20This%20compost%20eventually%20goes%20back%20to%20our%20fields%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kabir.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20shows%20the%20process%20of%20mulching%20and%20composting%20to%20the%2